===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[body]] with very small size; a [[fragment]].
# {{physics}} An [[elementary particle]] or [[subatomic particle]].
# {{linguistics}} A word that has a particular [[grammatical]] [[function]] but does not obviously belong to any particular [[part of speech]], such as the word ''to'' in English [[infinitive]]s or [[O]] as the [[vocative]] particle.

